---
// CoachConsole.astro — a sample AI-coaching exchange rendered as a chat
// console. Demonstrates the quality of Kaldon's AI coach without requiring
// the visitor to sign up. Static DOM; no live model behind it.
---

<div class="coach-console" aria-hidden="true">
  <!-- App bar -->
  <div class="coach-bar">
    <div class="coach-breadcrumb">
      <span class="coach-brand">Kaldon Coach</span>
      <span class="coach-sep">›</span>
      <span class="coach-context">Ironfield · Pricing decision</span>
    </div>
    <div class="coach-status">
      <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
      <span>Thinking</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Conversation -->
  <div class="coach-log">
    <div class="coach-turn user">
      <span class="coach-role">You</span>
      <p class="coach-body">Is $39 too high for the Ironfield 32oz launch? I'm seeing competitors at $29.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="coach-turn agent">
      <span class="coach-role coach-role-agent">Kaldon Coach</span>
      <p class="coach-body">
        You're looking at 1,247 competitor SKUs in insulated 32oz. Median sits at <span class="coach-emph-chalk">$34</span>. But bottles with a ceramic-lined interior command a <span class="coach-emph-gold">+42% premium</span>, averaging $49.
      </p>
      <p class="coach-body">
        Your $39 positions below premium but above commodity — a valid "accessible premium" slot. However, Walmart search data: <span class="coach-emph-chalk">78%</span> of "insulated water bottle" queries filter by $25–35.
      </p>
      <p class="coach-body">
        <span class="coach-emph-gold">Recommendation:</span> Launch at <span class="coach-emph-chalk">$34.99</span> on Amazon to capture high-intent search. Introduce a <span class="coach-emph-chalk">$44</span> premium variant on DTC for the ceramic-lined moat. Two-tier positioning, one supplier run.
      </p>
      <div class="coach-refs">
        <span class="coach-ref">Source · Amazon SP-API</span>
        <span class="coach-ref">Source · Walmart search data</span>
        <span class="coach-ref">Source · Competitor Vet Mode · 1,247 SKUs</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Input chrome (visual only, not interactive) -->
  <div class="coach-input">
    <span class="coach-input-hint">Ask a follow-up — margin, supplier, positioning, ads…</span>
    <span class="coach-input-key" aria-hidden="true">⌘ K</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .coach-console {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--deep-space);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .coach-console::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    padding: 1px;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,184,0,0.25), rgba(0,212,255,0.15) 60%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05));
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
            mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* App bar */
  .coach-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
  }
  .coach-breadcrumb {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ghost);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .coach-brand { color: var(--gold); }
  .coach-sep { color: rgba(139,139,163,0.35); }
  .coach-context { color: var(--chalk); }
  .coach-status {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ghost);
  }
  .coach-status .pulse-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; }

  /* Conversation */
  .coach-log {
    padding: 24px 24px 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .coach-turn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .coach-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ghost);
  }
  .coach-role-agent { color: var(--gold); }

  .coach-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .coach-turn.user .coach-body { color: var(--chalk); }

  .coach-emph-chalk {
    color: var(--chalk);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .coach-emph-gold {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .coach-refs {
    margin-top: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .coach-ref {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ghost);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* Input chrome */
  .coach-input {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
  }
  .coach-input-hint {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ghost);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .coach-input-key {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ghost);
    padding: 3px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--void);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
